<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.holocaustdenialontrial.org/evidence/evanscontent.asp">Expert Witness Report by Richard J. Evans</a> Complete text of Professor Evans' lengthy report on Irving's work in a number of areas.</li></ul></li>
